		<div class="resume-section">
			<h2>기술 스택</h2>
			<div class="section-content skills">
				<div class="skill-category">
					<h3>프론트엔드</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>HTML5 / CSS3</li>
						<li>JavaScript / TypeScript</li>
