				<div class="project-item">
					<h3>개인 포트폴리오 웹사이트</h3>
					<p>Astro, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS를 사용하여 개발한 개인 블로그 및 포트폴리오 웹사이트</p>
					<p><a href="https://github.com/yourusername/portfolio" target="_blank">GitHub 링크</a></p>
				</div>

				<div class="project-item">
					<h3>온라인 쇼핑몰</h3>
					<p>React, Node.js, MongoDB를 사용하여 개발한 e-커머스 플랫폼</p>
					<p><a href="https://github.com/yourusername/e-commerce" target="_blank">GitHub 링크</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="resume-section">
			<h2>자격증</h2>
			<div class="section-content">
				<ul class="certification-list">
					<li>AWS 공인 솔루션스 아키텍트 (2022)</li>
					<li>정보처리기사 (2018)</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	/* Resume_example.tsx 스타일 적용 */
	.text-center {
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.mb-8 {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.mt-2 {
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.mt-3 {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}
	
	.mt-4 {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}
	
	.mt-8 {
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	
	.grid {
		display: grid;
	}
	
	.gap-4 {
		gap: 1rem;
	}
	
	.gap-6 {
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.space-y-3 > * + * {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}
	
	.space-x-3 {
		column-gap: 0.75rem;
	}
	
	.flex {
		display: flex;
	}
	
	.justify-center {
		justify-content: center;
	}
	
	.items-center {
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.text-xs {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
	}
	
	.text-sm {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: #555;
	}
	
	.text-4xl {
		font-size: 2.25rem;
	}
	
	.font-medium {
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	
	.font-bold {
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	
	.uppercase {
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}
	
	.tracking-widest {
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}
	
	.whitespace-pre-line {
		white-space: pre-line;
	}
	
	.leading-relaxed {
		line-height: 1.625;
	}
	
	.section-label {
		color: #777;
	}
	
	.text-emoji {
		color: #666;
	}
	
	.text-emoji-sm {
		color: #666;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		margin-right: 0.25rem;
	}
	
	.text-gray-500 {
		color: #6b7280;
	}
	
	.hover-link {
		color: #0077cc;
		transition: color 0.2s, text-decoration 0.2s;
	}
	
	.hover-link:hover {
		color: #005fa3;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	
	.hover-link-sm {
		color: #0077cc;
		transition: color 0.2s, text-decoration 0.2s;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
	}
	
	.hover-link-sm:hover {
		color: #005fa3;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	
	.contact-info-inline {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: #6b7280;
	}
	
	/* 기존 스타일 오버라이드 */
	.resume-header {
		border-bottom: none;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	
	.profile-image-container {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.profile-image {
		width: 160px;
		height: 160px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		border: 3px solid #f0f0f0;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	
	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.grid-cols-1 {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(1, minmax(0, 1fr));
		}
		
		.md\:grid-cols-3 {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		}
		
		.md\:col-span-1 {
			grid-column: span 1 / span 1;
		}
		
		.md\:col-span-2 {
			grid-column: span 2 / span 2;
		}
		
		.md\:text-5xl {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
	}
	
	.resume-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		background-color: white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.resume-section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.resume-section h2 {
		border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #444;
	}

	.section-content {
		padding: 1rem 0;
	}

	.skills {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.skill-category h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: #555;
	}

	.skill-category ul {
		list-style-type: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.skill-category li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		background-color: #f8f8f8;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.experience-item, .education-item, .project-item {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.experience-header, .education-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: baseline;
	}

	.experience-header h3, .education-header h3, .project-item h3 {
		margin: 0;
		color: #333;
	}

	.period {
		color: #666;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.position {
		color: #555;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.responsibilities {
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.responsibilities li {
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.project-item p {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.certification-list {
		list-style-type: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.certification-list li {
		background-color: #f8f8f8;
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	a {
		color: #0077cc;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.profile-section {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: flex-start;
		}

		.profile-image {
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
		}

		.skills {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.experience-header, .education-header {
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.period {
			margin-top: 0.25rem;
		}
	}

	.job-title {
		margin: 0.2rem 0 !important;
		padding: 0 !important;
		font-weight: 500;
	}
</style> 